                <div class="flex justify-center space-x-4 mb-8">
                    <button onclick="toggleAnalysis('limitations')" id="btn-limitations" class="px-6 py-2 rounded-full font-medium text-sm transition-all bg-slate-800 text-white shadow-md">Keterbatasan (Limitations)</button>
                    <button onclick="toggleAnalysis('opportunities')" id="btn-opportunities" class="px-6 py-2 rounded-full font-medium text-sm transition-all bg-white text-slate-600 border border-slate-300 hover:bg-slate-50">Peluang (Future Work)</button>
                </div>

                <div id="content-limitations" class="bg-red-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-red-100 animate-fade-in">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-red-800 mb-4 flex items-center">
                        <span class="mr-2">‚ö†Ô∏è</span> Batasan Desain AXI-Lite
                    </h3>
                    <ul class="space-y-4">
                        <li class="flex items-start bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0 h-6 w-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 text-red-600 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold mt-0.5">1</div>
                            <div class="ml-4">
                                <h4 class="text-md font-semibold text-slate-800">Tidak Mendukung Burst Mode</h4>
                                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">AXI-Lite hanya mendukung single transaction. Transfer data besar (seperti memcpy) akan mengalami overhead handshake yang tinggi di setiap kata data.</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0 h-6 w-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 text-red-600 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold mt-0.5">2</div>
                            <div class="ml-4">
                                <h4 class="text-md font-semibold text-slate-800">Bus Width Tetap</h4>
                                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Implementasi ini terpaku pada lebar data 32-bit, membatasi bandwidth potensial jika core di-upgrade ke 64-bit di masa depan.</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div id="content-opportunities" class="hidden bg-green-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-green-100 animate-fade-in">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-800 mb-4 flex items-center">
                        <span class="mr-2">üöÄ</span> Peluang Pengembangan
                    </h3>
                    <ul class="space-y-4">
                        <li class="flex items-start bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0 h-6 w-6 rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-600 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold mt-0.5">1</div>
                            <div class="ml-4">
                                <h4 class="text-md font-semibold text-slate-800">Direct Memory Access (DMA)</h4>
                                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Menambahkan kontroler DMA untuk menangani transfer data memori-ke-periferal tanpa membebani CPU, mengatasi kelemahan burst mode.</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0 h-6 w-6 rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-600 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold mt-0.5">2</div>
                            <div class="ml-4">
                                <h4 class="text-md font-semibold text-slate-800">Implementasi Cache L1</h4>
                                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Menambahkan Instruction Cache untuk mengurangi frekuensi akses bus ke memori utama, meningkatkan IPC (Instructions Per Cycle).</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>

